* Table 5.3.
* Regression DD Estimates of MLDA-Induced Deaths among 18-20 Year Olds, from 1970-1983, controlling for Beer Taxes

xi: reg mrate legal 
outreg2  beertax using "table53.xls", replace bdec(2) sdec(2) excel noaster cttop("`i'")

